starving to death.

598
01:12:43,470 --> 01:12:44,760
I'm hungry too.

599
01:12:45,810 --> 01:12:48,140
Bacurau has food and water. Let's go.

600
01:12:48,350 --> 01:12:50,890
People there know
all you do for them.

601
01:12:51,010 --> 01:12:52,180
You're important.

602
