617
01:18:31,600 --> 01:18:32,640
Martina.

618
01:18:32,810 --> 01:18:33,970
Sebastiana.

619
01:18:34,890 --> 01:18:36,350
Erivaldo and his kids.

620
01:18:36,510 --> 01:18:37,470
José.

621
01:18:38,640 --> 01:18:39,600
Me.

622
