707
01:55:16,350 --> 01:55:18,890
Stand up, you bastard. I've got you.

708
01:55:19,140 --> 01:55:21,930
What are you doing
on my land, you scum?

709
01:56:45,140 --> 01:56:47,220
<i>Rivanildo Gomes dos Santos.</i>

710
01:56:48,430 --> 01:56:50,300
<i>Flávio Tavares Nascimento.</i>

